review: Really enjoyed my experience in the room. Very intriguing and challenging. I look forward to going back.

room_title: Escape room "Meltdown" by Escape the Room Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: First experience. Getting started was awkward. During the last 30 minutes, we got going. Will do again! Challenging and fun. Ask for clues early if you feel stuck.

room_title: Escape room "Meltdown" by Escape the Room Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: Was supposed to be 3 people told in our group but one didn't show so it was only 2 of us We did Meltdown room and it was challenging but we ended up escaping with 55 seconds left. Staff was extremely helpful throughout.
